      "segmentNumber": 1,
      "visualDescription": "A vibrant 2D anime illustration capturing a quiet bedroom scene at night. A young boy, around seven years old, sits on his bed, slightly huddled. His eyes are wide with a touch of apprehension. He clutches a well-worn, fluffy brown teddy bear tightly to his chest. Soft, dim light from a small nightlight glows faintly in the background, casting gentle, long shadows on the wall, hinting at a cozy but slightly mysterious atmosphere. Clean line art, warm but subdued colors.",
      "dialogueOrNarration": "Leo is a young boy. He is eight years old. [pause] Every night, Leo feels scared in his room. It gets very dark. Long shadows move on the walls. Leo imagines monsters in these shadows. His heart beats fast. He sits on his bed. He holds his old, soft teddy bear. The bear is brown. A small nightlight shines softly. It gives a faint, warm glow. This light makes the room a little less scary. [softly] Leo hugs his bear very tightly. The bear helps him feel safe. He closes his eyes. He tries to sleep. The night is long, but Leo has his special bear.",
      "subtitle": "Leo is a young boy. He is eight years old. Every night, Leo feels scared in his room. It gets very dark. Long shadows move on the walls. Leo imagines monsters in these shadows. His heart beats fast. He sits on his bed. He holds his old, soft teddy bear. The bear is brown. A small nightlight shines softly. It gives a faint, warm glow. This light makes the room a little less scary. Leo hugs his bear very tightly. The bear helps him feel safe. He closes his eyes. He tries to sleep. The night is long, but Leo has his special bear.\nLeo là một cậu bé. Cậu bé tám tuổi. Mỗi đêm, Leo cảm thấy sợ hãi trong phòng của mình. Trời trở nên rất tối. Những bóng tối dài di chuyển trên tường. Leo tưởng tượng ra quái vật trong những bóng tối này. Tim cậu đập nhanh. Cậu ngồi trên giường. Cậu ôm chú gấu bông cũ mềm của mình. Chú gấu có màu nâu. Một chiếc đèn ngủ nhỏ chiếu sáng nhẹ nhàng. Nó tỏa ra ánh sáng mờ ảo, ấm áp. Ánh sáng này làm căn phòng bớt đáng sợ một chút. Leo ôm chú gấu của mình thật chặt. Chú gấu giúp cậu cảm thấy an toàn. Cậu nhắm mắt lại. Cậu cố gắng ngủ. Đêm dài, nhưng Leo có chú gấu đặc biệt của mình.",
